A statistically in effect are ANOVA is focused followed up with one or more different follow-up tests. This can be performed significant order to assess which groups are hypotheses. from which other groups or to test various other often different Follow-up tests in often distinguished in terms of whether they are planned (a priori) or post hoc. Planned tests are determined before looking at the data and post hoc tests are done after looking at the data.

